n&quot;\">开发者大会最佳讲师、最佳讲义</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">获得者；</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年度开源项目之一</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">AgileUML</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的主架设计师。更重要的是他是一位快乐的实用主义程序员。虽然他热衷于软件开发技术与敏捷开发实践。但</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是能真正吸引他的是程序与使用者交流和沟通的能力。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Jobs</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是实用开发的“永久消费者”，几乎在任何地方，都可以找到软件开发哲学的灵感。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">当不沉浸在编程之乐时，他喜欢在</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">DotA</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">世界里充当一名战队的组织者，在那里，人们叫他</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Rails</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">！</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--> \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4506,'陈勇',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'麦思博（msup）有限公司资深顾问',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">讲师背景<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" zh-cn;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\"=\"\" lang=\"EN-US\">17年研发、管理及咨询经验，擅长在实际环境中灵活应用各种研发方法论<br />具有丰富的工程技术与项目管理实践经验，从其程序员、项目经理、CMMI/FPA功能点估算/敏捷咨询师、事业部总监、副总经理等各种技术与管理岗位获得的一手经验，令其可以站在企业管理者的高度，以更广的视角来理解敏捷开发，并能配合和推动非研发部门协作推广敏捷。<br />曾以技术骨干和项目经理等身份，组织和承担开发了国庆50周年直升机编队指挥系统、空军一基地GPS数据源系统、清华同方CCTV数字电视条件接收系统、航空材料研究院无损检测系统等项目。<br />曾在清华同方、普天集团、亚信科技等企业担任EPG骨干、组长；曾在斯福泰克、DNV ITGS等机构担任CMMI/功能点/敏捷开发咨询师。<br />在任泰克赛尔软件公司中国部门的咨询总监、ALM事业部总监、副总经理期间，主管研发管理工具的市场、销售、支持与咨询活动，在盛大、金山、腾讯、汉王科技等知名企业深入推动其工具应用与实施活动。<br />现任国际外包管理协会（IIOM）中国区CTO和咨询总监，并作为产品经理、架构师带领一个小型团队，从事“火星人敏捷开发在线平台”的研发工作，其中融合了功能点、用例等各种工程方法。很多课程与咨询中的最佳实践，均来自于其之前及当前参与的实际项目的一线实践。<br />荣获2012年度中国十大杰出IT博客（唯一的管理博客），CSDN阅读量首位的管理类博客。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:zh-cn;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></span><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colba