mily:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">讲师背景<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">《软件调试》一书的作者，《程序员》杂志调试之剑栏目作者，高端调试网站（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">ADVDBG.ORG</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）的创始人。毕业于上海交通大学信息与控制工程系，长期从</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">事软件开发和研究工作，对</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"> IA-32 </span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">架构、操作系统内核、驱动程序、尤其是软件调试有较深入研究。从</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年开始公开讲授</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">“Windows</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">内核及高级调试</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">课程，曾在微软的</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Webcast </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和各种技术会议上做过《</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Windows Vista</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">内核演进》、《调试之剑》（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年中国软件技术大会）、《感受和思考调试器的威力》（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">CSDN SD2.0</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">大会）、《</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Windows</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">启动过程》、《如何诊断和调试蓝屏错误》、《</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Windows</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">体系结构</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">——</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">从操作系统的角度》（以上三个讲座都是微软</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"> “</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">深入研究</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Windows</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">内部原理系列</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的一部分）等。翻译（合译）作品有《观止</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">——</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">微软创建</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">NT</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和未来的夺命狂奔》、《数据挖掘原理》、《机器学习》、</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">《人工智能：复杂问题求解的结构和策略》等。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagina