e=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">统、科技部信产部重大专项</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Elastos</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">网络操作系统；企业级如被搜狐用之奥运的</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">TVie</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">视频直播、被移动用之世博的</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">TrafficCast</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">实时路况，以</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">及失败的</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">1800helpers</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">比价购物搜索引擎、</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Bluevees</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">农民工社区等。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">作