:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">V2</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）及之二的《就这么做创新》（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">V1</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">），并以新维私塾为平台为中国一线精英提供做</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">产品或做创新的培训咨询。曾在政界如中央国家机关党校、北上广深等十几个高新区；学界如北大、清华、中科院等；商界如</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">强外企的微软、谷歌、施耐德电</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">气等；国企的移动、东软、</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">TCL</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">等；民企的百度、用友、携程等；大会如中国计算机大会、全国高校电子商务大会、全球互动专家讲坛等做过数百场演讲</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">培训</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"> /</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">咨询。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">历任微软总部开发主管</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">产品经理、科泰产品副总裁、美慧首席产品官</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">首席运营官、蓝巍</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。历兼中国计算机学会</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">YOCSEF</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">全国副主席。历读北大计算机本科、美国</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Syracuse </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">大学计算机硕士、华盛顿大学</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">EMBA</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4513,'Forest',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'曾在加拿大蒙特利尔银行（BMO）担任顾问实施',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">讲师背景<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">超过二十年数据库（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">RDB</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">），数据仓库（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">DW</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">），商务智能（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">BI</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）及数据挖掘（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">DM</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）方面的设计，开发，管理经验，熟悉全过程系统架构</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">(3- Tir/Multi-Tir Architecture)</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，精通实时</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">DW</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">ETL</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的设计与开发熟悉业界领先的</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">DW/BI/DM</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">技术，如</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">DB2, Informatica</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">OWB, COGNOS</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">DISCOVERER,SAS,ODM</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">等，项目涉及银行，电讯，在线游戏、证券。应用系统架构技术设计，开发，实施大规模的，多种异构数据源的，实时的数据仓库和报表系统。在多年的理论探索与大量的实践中，积累了丰富和独到的经验，包括异构数据互联；逻辑和物理建模；数据库服务器规划，安</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">装，配置，优化，升级，备份和恢复；</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">ETL/ ROLAP/MOLAP</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">设计；</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">BI</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">报表方案设计；以及数据挖掘的分析与建模。掌握北美先进的项目管理经验，曾在加拿大蒙特利尔银行（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">BMO</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">），加拿大研科</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">电讯公司（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">TELUS </span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）等大型机构有多个大型项目设计，开发，实施和迁移经验。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4514,'陈钧',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'曾担任美国银行系统架构师',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">讲师背景<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">超过十五年的软件开发经验，互联网框架设计、软件开发及其管理，特别在使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">J2EE</span>和\r\n其他当代网络技术开发和建设基础平台系统方面有丰富经验。近<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>年的美国银行系统架构师工作经历，期间负责设计、建设公司网络应用软件的基础平台，具有高度可扩展性，成为企业<span lang=\"EN-US\">RAD</span>（快速应用软件开发）的基础设施。这个单点登录的基础设施 为以网络为基 础商用软件开发提供了共同的架构及功能，如认证，授权，菜单设定，用户个性化，<span lang=\"EN-US\">session</span>管理，交易处理，报表生成，多层次缓存（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Web</span>服务器、应用 服务器和数据库服\r\n器），预设报表生成及共享，<span lang=\"EN-US\">mail</span>，具有<span lang=\"EN-US\">MVC</span>及<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hibernate</span>的设计思想。该平台上前后曾有<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>个业务应用程序运行。其独特的设计大大简化商用软\r\n件开发的过程，极大的降低了开发成本，节省了公司数百万美元的软件开发费用</span><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4515,'李胜',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Oready技术支持 Oracle技能传授讲师',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">讲师背景<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">技术支持项目（列出仅为<span lang=\"EN-US\">95</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">96</span>年间的部分技术服务项目）</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">中国银行业务系统压力测试</span></strong><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">环境：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\nSOLARIS8 + Oracle9i<br />\r\n</span>用户要进行业务系统 设备选型，选择服务器厂商为<span lang=\"EN-US\">IBM</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">SUN</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">HP</span>，作为<span lang=\"EN-US\">SUN</span>总代的合作伙伴，我们协助客户搭建了测试平台，并且根据用户需求进行多种不同大批次、大数据\r\n量的压力测试，经过对数据库系统的调整，测试结果中多项指标在三大厂商中排名第一，使用户在选择服务器时更趋向于使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">SUN</span>的主机系统。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">中国建设银行银联系统数据迁移</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">环境：<span lang=\"EN-US\"> AIX\r\n+ Oracle9i<br />\r\n</span>用户需要对银联的旧系统作 数据库升级与迁移，数据库从<span lang=\"EN-US\">8i</span>升级到<span lang=\"EN-US\">9i</span>，服务器也更换为更高配置的服务器，迁移时间有严格要求，<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>小时内迁移完成，而用户的数据量较大（<span lang=\"EN-US\">TB</span>级），必 须一次迁移成功。根据用户需求，制定了详细的迁移方案及撤销方案，即使迁移不能顺利完成，也可以完好的将应用撤销回原系统，不存在任何风险。经过几次测试\r\n演练，选择了最快最安全的实施步骤，最终实施时只使用了<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>小时就完成完全的迁移，系统提前切换成功。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">北京慧聪网数据库性能优化</span></strong><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">环境：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\nSOLARIS9 + Oracle9i RAC<br />\r\n</span>用户的网站由于并发用户过大，总是导致无法登陆以及页面无法显示的错误，后台数据库是<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle9i</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">RAC</span>，通过对用户应用的了解后，针对性的对后台数据库做了性能上的调整，并针对部分应用做了修改后一切正常。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">畅捷公司数据库优化</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">环境：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\nSOLARIS8 + Oracle9i<br />\r\n</span>负责畅捷公司计费数据库的性能优化，使其公司运行在该数据库上的应用运行性能有明显改善，同时对数据库中潜在的问题也进行了处理，减少了该数据库需要停机的次数。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">北京市第六医院数据库灾难恢复和性能调优</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">环境：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\nWindows2000 + Oracle9i RAC + HIS</span>系统<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span>用户数据库由于遇到<span lang=\"EN-US\">windows</span>上的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">bug</span>，导致数据库一个数据文件无法使用，经过使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span>的内部恢复工具将用户的数据完全恢复，并针对应用做了数据库的调整优化，使用户的数据库性能大大的得到了提高，现医院的所有<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span>服务均由我们提供。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">河南网通计费、<span lang=\"EN-US\">97</span>系统巡检</span></strong><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">环境：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\nIBM AIX4.3.3 + Oracle8i / HP-UX11.0 + Oracle8i / Tru64 UNIX + 7.3.2.3<br />\r\n</span>对 河南北部<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>个地市的网通计费和<span lang=\"EN-US\">97</span>数据库进行巡检，根据<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span>的标准文档为用户提交巡检报告。在巡检过程中对用户的数据库进行详细的信息收集，并给 予准确完整的分析报告和建议，对一些潜在的问题为用户进行了现场的解决或者给出了详细的解决建议，对影响较大的问题在报告中进行了详细的说明，以便用户能\r\n够更多的了解自己数据库所存在的问题，更好更及时的解决现在存在的问题。由于报告准确及时，并且与用户有良好的沟通，得到了各地市用户的好评。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">国家电力通讯公司安装与优化</span></strong><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">环境：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\nTru64 UNIX + Oracle8i<br />\r\n</span>根据用户需求，完成<span lang=\"EN-US\">TRU64</span>系统上<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle8i</span>数据库的安装和配置优化。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">河南新乡网通故障处理</span></strong><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">环境：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\nIBM AIX4.3.3 + Oracle8i ( OPS )<br />\r\n</span>新乡网通计费数据库在运行过程中，出现过两次比较严重的故障，故障造成单个节点不能正常的关闭（和启动，两种故障各遇到一次），根据用户描述的故障状态，判断故障可能的原因，对数据库中的潜在错误进行了纠正，解决了故障，并使用户的数据库没有再发生过类似的故障。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">山西网通性能调整</span></strong><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">环境：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\nIBM AIX4.3.3 + Oracle8i<br />\r\n</span>由于为山西网通做过 多次培训，对网通数据库系统比较熟悉，所以多次为用户提供故障的解决方案。另外，由于山西网通计费数据库数据量巨大（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>个<span lang=\"EN-US\">T</span>以上），所以在月末出帐的时候 性能有明显的问题，同时伴随着出现一些回滚段相关的错误，通过对月末时段的数据库统计信息收集，了解用户的业务情况，对数据库提供了一系列优化方案，并指\r\n导用户完成优化过程。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">中海油公司数据库应用系统实施顾问</span></strong><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">用户将要开发一套基于<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span>数据库的<span lang=\"EN-US\">OA</span>应用系统，但对于<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\nOracle</span>数据库在整体架构中的设计和使用并不是很清楚，对于<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span>数据库的能力也不太熟悉，所以邀请作为项目实施顾问参与整体项目方案的设计讨\r\n论。在讨论会上，配合数据库软件供应商，为用户详细讲解了<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span>数据库的一些特点和长处，使用户确定了采纳<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span>数据库存储数据的信心，同时 也协助用户完善整体系统的方案设计，使用户最终确定了整体系统的架构。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\">2001.10 – 2003.1 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体\">北京宇思时代软件技术有限公司</span></strong><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">技术开发部<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span>数据库工程师<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span>负责<span lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span>数据库、<span lang=\"EN-US\">iAS</span>、<span lang=