-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">身份认证，自建</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">CA</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">中心进行管理。同时也跟国际上著名的</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">CA</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">认证公司，如</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"> verisign,globalsign</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">有密切的合作关系。从</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">PKI</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">体系到</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">PKI</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">实践都有丰富的经验和认识。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0