工程硕士，微软最有价值专家，微软<span lang=\"EN-US\">MSDN</span>特约讲师。曾于微软亚洲工程院<span lang=\"EN-US\">MSN</span>组工作，现任中国网通四分公司技术支持与项目部开发经理。具有多年电信系统与<span lang=\"EN-US\">OA</span>系统。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4528,'Ray Zhang',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'微软Excel产品组开发经理',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">讲师背景<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">多年工作于互联网和软件产品一线，经历了从单机软件、企业信息化、互联网、物联网和大数据等近<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>年来<span lang=\"EN-US\">IT</span>产业的起起落落，对产品设计与互联网运营有较为丰富的经验和独到的见解。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">曾任微软公司开发技术经理，致力于为中国顶尖的软件企业提供解决方案架构咨询。亦曾任微软<span lang=\"EN-US\">Excel</span>产品主管，负责<span lang=\"EN-US\">Excel&amp;BI</span>产品多个版本的规划设计与研发管理，作为<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mac</span>事业部与<span lang=\"EN-US\">Excel</span>核心产品组的第一位华人产品经理，他带领团队成功发布了多个软件产品版本，受到全球多个国家<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>地区用户的普遍欢迎。张大磊亦曾创立北京若云兄弟科技有限公司，在互联网个性化推荐服务、智慧城市建设、传统行业互联网化、物联网与大数据分析等多个领域成功设计和运营了多个商业产品，创造了较大的社会价值和经济价值。张大磊带领的团队被评为中国电信十大开发者、诺基亚<span lang=\"EN-US\">NEIC</span>首批训练团成员，所发布的移动互联网 产品也屡次斩获微软开发者大赛大奖和苹果<span lang=\"EN-US\">AppStore\r\nTop10</span>榜单推荐。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">作为从事过多年产品开发的创业人<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>在业余时间，组织参与了一些技术俱乐部和社会志愿者组织，与全国各地的软件企业、开发者社区、志愿者社区保持联系，他还是微软金牌讲师评委与<span lang=\"EN-US\">TechED</span>最受欢迎讲师，同时辅导过包括微软、惠普、金山、神州数码、浪潮、用友、中国移动在内的多家软件和互联网企业的产品规划设计与团队管理人员。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4529,'陈扬',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'曾任Oracle公司开发测试主管、曾任微软公司开发测试主管',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <