><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">安捷伦</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">(Agilent),</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">甲骨文软件公司</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">(Oracle )</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">从事过二十年的新产品市场调研</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">定义规划，市推广等产品管理工作，并负责新业务规划和企业战略联盟管理，擅长将跨国公司产品创新流程在中国本地实践，具有丰富的新产品和业务创新和管理经验。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">汪宁先生</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">1989</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年加入中国惠普公司，参与建立中国惠普研发实验室并作为第一位软件研发发工程师被派往美国惠普试验室工作</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">加入新产品研究开发小组并学习新产品研发管理工作。回国后</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">汪宁先生作为研发经理负责开发出了数款针对中国通讯市场需求的通讯新产品</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">获得惠普公司嘉奖。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"> 1996</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年起任第一位中国惠普公司产品经理</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">负责全球通讯开关产品的新产品概念测试</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">产品定义及新产品上市推广和新市场开发</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">成功地在亚洲、欧洲和美国等地组织了新产品的市场调研和推广发布会。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* St