ne-height:\r\n150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Danie</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">具有多年的敏捷项目（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Scrum &amp; XP</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）实践经验以及丰富的带队经验。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\nDanie</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">老师于</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月创建了</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Irdeto</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">上海研发团队，并将</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Scrum</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">XP</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">成功引入了团队。目前该团队主要负责数百万美金级别的大型付费媒体计费及客户关系管理系统的开发及维护，四年中成功发布产品的两个新版本。系统现在在美洲、欧洲以及亚洲的许多国家运行。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\nDanie </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">一直致力于将海外的敏捷思想、理论及方法以及实践介绍到国内，帮助国内的软件团队高效并有趣地工作，真正为客户创造价值。作为敏捷社区的活跃分子，</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Daniel</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">通过博客、</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">InfoQ</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">以及讨论组等宣传敏捷。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Daniel</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">经常受邀到各个会议中针对敏捷话题进行演讲，他是敏捷中国</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的讲师，并受邀参加</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">QCon</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">北京</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">以及在</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">CSDN</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">举办的软件开发</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">2.0</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">大会</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">等中作关于敏捷的演讲。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4534,'David.Zhang',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'曾任IBM中国有限公司部门经理，中国惠普有限公司项目管理部总监',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 