US\">Web</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">开发的一线技术人员和培训讲师。一直致力于对</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">HTML</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">JavaScript</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">CSS</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">jQuery</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">等</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Web</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">开发技术的研究和实践，在</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">HTML</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">页面的优化与用户体验的研究，以及页面框架搭建、数据流向分析、页面静态优化等方面都拥有丰富的实践经验。自</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">HTML 5</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&