ight:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">技术研究和应用开发工作，特别是在</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">中国公司的</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年时间里，分别在顾问咨询部、技术服务部担任资深技术顾问。在银行、电信、政府等行业和部门参与了多个大型</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">IT</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">系统的建设，提供了体系结构设计、数据库设计、应用开发设计指导、性能优化、数据备份恢复、容灾系统建设、数据仓库系统建设、数据库安全性等领域的咨询和技术支持服务，并为国内主要软件开发商和集成商进行过多场</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\" lang=\"EN-US\">Oracle</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">高级技术应用培训和交流活动。</span><span class=\"style2\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom