"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%\">北京大学<span style=\"color:black\">博士后，第一届中国软件业十大杰出青年候选人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:black\">专著《不是三维——软件项目的设计、开发与管理》与《消息设计与开发：分布式应用开发的核心技术》作者<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:black\">。<br />云计算数据基础设施倡导者与研究者，第十六届世界计算机大会电子商务大会数据管理分会主席，中国青年科技工作者协会第二届会员，中小企业创新基金评审专家，中国软件技术大会特邀讲师。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:black\"><br />现从事云计算，<span lang=\"EN-US\">NoSQL</span>与大数据，企业<span lang=\"EN-US\">IT</span>架构、企业数据架构以及信息系统设计开发等方面的研究与实践工作，涉及金融、电信及政府等多个行业。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:black\"><br />曾任空间信息领域教师，获福建省，山东省引进高级人才计划。<span lang=\"EN-US\">1992</span>年起从事软件的设计、开发与管理工作，自<span lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span>年起，在北美从事软件系统分析与设计工作近七年之久，迄今为止，共负责、参与国内外大中型软件项目<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>多项，历任中国大中型<span lang=\"EN-US\">IT</span>企业总工程师，技术管理部部长，事业部副总经理，<span lang=\"EN-US\">BI</span>首席架构师，软件开发总监及云计算与大数据首席架构师等职。共在国内外发表科技论文<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>余篇，多篇获奖，并被美国《工程索引》<span lang=\"EN-US\">EI</span>检索<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>篇。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--><p class=\"p0\" style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><!--EndFragment--></span><!--EndFragment-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4598,'凌棕',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'高级工程师/科学家',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">凌棕博士，</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">美国</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\" lang=\"EN-US\">IBM</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">公司软件集团 高级工程师</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\" lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">科学家<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">凌棕博士早年毕业于</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\" lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.ustc.edu.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext;\r\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">中国科学技术大学</span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">，然后赴美留学并获电子工程博士学位<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>其后至今应聘就职于座落在美国北加州<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>硅谷<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>圣何西市的</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\" lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.almaden.ibm.com/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext;mso-fareast-language:\r\nZH-CN;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">IBM Almaden</span><span style=\"color:windowtext;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;text-decoration:\r\nnone;text-underline:none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">研究中心</span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">。</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-language:\r\nZH-CN\">在<span lang=\"EN-US\">IBM</span>公司的任职工作中<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>凌棕博士主要致力于云存储数据管理系统的设计开发和性能评估<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>以及商务数据系统灾难恢复管理等方面的研究<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>是<span lang=\"EN-US\"> IBM</span>公司电子商务基础软件和数据存储管理系统开发的技术带头人，并多次获得由美国总统签发的嘉奖函与奖章。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">凌棕博士经常在各种大型国际会议、公司内外部研讨会、和技术培训班上宣讲介绍<span lang=\"EN-US\"> IBM</span>的先进技术。曾在全球范围内为欧洲、北美、亚太地区超过<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>个国家的<span lang=\"EN-US\"> IBM</span>员工和合作伙伴进行过技术培训<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>并长期执教于<span lang=\"EN-US\">IBM</span>全球电子商务大学。</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">近年来<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Tms Rmn&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">作为<span lang=\"EN-US\"> IBM</span>公司的杰出校园大使和多所高校的兼职教授<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>凌棕博士不但为美国硅谷地区的斯坦福大学和加州大学伯克利分校开设专题技术课程，还为中国高校的软件学院、信息学院、和管理学院的师生开设了技术选修课程</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">，并数度应邀在中国软件技术年会，<span lang=\"EN-US\">IBM</span>中国软件开发者年会，及高等院校、研究所等不同场合做专题报告<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>结合从事研发、管理工作的切身经历<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>既讲授关于信息系统工程的实用技术<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>又传播<span lang=\"EN-US\">IBM</span>公司逾百年来经久不衰的创新机制、运作规则和企业文化。</span><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4599,'Marty Cagan',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'author of &lt;&lt;Inspired: How to Create Products Customers',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'<!--[if !mso]>\r\n<style>\r\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Marty\r\nCagan is the author of &lt;&lt;Inspired: How to Create Products Customers\r\nLove&gt;&gt;. During the course of the past 30 years, Marty Cagan has served as\r\nan executive responsible for defining and building products for some of the\r\nmost successful companies in the world, including Hewlett-Packard, Netscape\r\nCommunications, America Online, and eBay.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Before founding the Silicon Valley Product Group to pursue his\r\ninterests in helping others create successful products through his writing,\r\nspeaking, and training, Marty was most recently senior vice-president of\r\nproduct management and design for eBay, where he was responsible for defining\r\nproducts and services for the company’s global e-commerce trading site.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Marty began his career at Hewlett-Packard Laboratories conducting\r\nresearch on software technology, and building several software products for\r\nother software developers.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">After HP, Marty joined a then young Netscape Communications\r\nCorporation, where he had the opportunity to participate in the birth of the\r\nInternet industry. Martin worked directly for co-founder Marc Andreessen, where\r\nhe was vice-president for Netscape’s platform and tools, and later e-commerce\r\napplications, and worked to help Internet start-ups and Fortune 500 companies\r\nalike to understand and utilize the newly emerging technology.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">During his career, Marty has personally performed and managed most\r\nof the roles of a modern software product organization, including product\r\nmanagement, software development, product marketing, user interface design,\r\nusability engineering, technical writing, software testing, engineering\r\nmanagement, and general management.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:shapedefaults v:ext=\"edit\" spidmax=\"1027\"/>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:shapelayout v:ext=\"edit\">\r\n  <o:idmap v:ext=\"edit\" data=\"1\"/>\r\n </o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL),(4600,'张镭',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'运营总监',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1415779950,1415779950,1,1,NULL,NULL,'\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-right:28.7pt;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:left;line-height:150%;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-other\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><b>讲师背景</b><br /></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-right:28.7pt;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:left;line-height:150%;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-other\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">现任美国某著名跨国公司服务集团运营总监，致力于组织内部的服务业务的运作管理和项目管理。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-right:28.7pt;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:left;line-height:150%;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-other\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">张老师于</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">1994</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">年加入</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">IBM</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（中国）有限公司，服务于全球服务部（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">IGS</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">），担任过系统分析工程师、项目经理、全球服务部高级项目经理及高级部门经理等职务，参与了数十个大、中、小型项目的售前、售后工作，并负责</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">IBM</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">全球服务方法论在中国的具体实施。</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-right:28.7pt;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:left;line-height:150%;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-other\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">年，张老师加入中国惠普有限公司，历任项目总监、项目管理部总监，运营管理部总监，负责应用服务业务的运营管理工作。张先生长期致力于大型项目的管理实施工作，具有丰富的实战经验和操作能力。张先生还就</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">IT</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">运营管理和项目管理知识体系做过多次的公开和内部培训。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-right:28.7pt;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:left;line-height:150%;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-other\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi